('', 'Alsatian museum', 'Strasbourg', '<iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d168968.42259219624!2d7.6216654371894315!3d48.56902817129283!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x4796c8495e18b2c1%3A0x971a483118e7241f!2sStrasbourg!5e0!3m2!1sfr!2sfr!4v1501773022940" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 0, 0, 'Visites', 'Discover the arts and popular traditions in Alsace through this museum that will make you travel in time.', '', 'Alsatian museum'),
('', 'Annecy et ses environs', 'Haute-Savoie', '<iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d708948.3202509595!2d5.863210308888751!3d46.044528060055356!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x478c09f4796a177d%3A0x308ab2ae4b92a20!2sHaute-Savoie!5e0!3m2!1sfr!2sfr!4v1501844702883" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 0, 0, 'Visites', 'Visit Annecy.\r\nNicknamed the "Venice of the Alps".\r\nHow was it lived in the Middle Ages? What about water, sewage, sanitation? To discover the medieval life, going in search of the signs of the past time. Borrow secret and discrete passages ...\r\n... Or why not look at Annecy with the eyes of Jean Jacques Rousseau, or go in the footsteps of Saint Francis de Sales exploring the important places of the Counter Reformation?\r\n<br>\r\nVisit the castle of Annecy and the old prisons:\r\nTwo historical monuments, testimonies of a city life and court, looking for their secrets. But also to discover a rich museum, sheltered in the castle: collection of furniture, statues, paintings of mountain ...\r\n<br>\r\nLake Annecy and neighboring castles:\r\nStroll around the lake, discover scenic views, hamlets, chapels and picturesque castles. But also admire this lake with the changing atmosphere and the many colors, known to be the purest of Europe.', '', 'Annecy et ses environs'),
