('', 'Atelier de cuisine du ChÃ¢teau Kirwan', 'Bordeaux', '<iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d4709.709934554633!2d-0.6610905418737322!3d45.027188051904105!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x4801d5b78d9a4311%3A0x496dfccf4927abe2!2sCh%C3%A2teau+Kirwan!5e0!3m2!1sfr!2sfr!4v1499850000728" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 127, 3, 'French-Gastronomy', 'Cooking lovers, join the Chef StÃ©phanie Bottreau (Cook Nâ€™Tinem) at ChÃ¢teau Kirwan.\r\n<br>\r\nLet us prove you how fun and easy cooking can be. Let us teach you how to make delicious recipes, from main courses to dessertsâ€¦ with a lot of tasting along the way.\r\n<br>\r\nPut on your chefâ€™s hat and have an enjoyable time learning all the cooking secrets of Chef StÃ©phanie.\r\nThe cuisine is simple but original and it is always made up of seasonal and local products.\r\n\r\n<br>\r\nPrice\r\nFrom 2 to 4 people: 127â‚¬/ pers\r\n\r\n<br>\r\nOPEN DAYS\r\n\r\nFrom 02/01/2017 until 21/12/2017\r\nOpen daily\r\n<br>\r\nADDRESS\r\n\r\n33460 CANTENAC\r\n\r\nRÃ©gion viticole MÃ©doc\r\n', 'From 02/01/2017 until 21/12/2017 Open daily', 'ATELIER DE CUISINE DU CHÃ‚TEAU KIRWAN'),
('', 'Barrage Vauban', 'Strasbourg', '<iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2639.579476864745!2d7.735860950671173!3d48.579602528148754!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x4796c9b4cece3f43%3A0xa2ad7688a014153e!2sBarrage+Vauban!5e0!3m2!1sfr!2sfr!4v1501586638254" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 200, 2, 'Visites', '', 'Tous les jours', 'Barrage Vauban'),
('', 'Basque Cooking Class in Biarritz', 'Biarritz', '<iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2897.1639432616166!2d-1.5651006850948714!3d43.4362918744486!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0xd5114ff10c8c287%3A0xe2864aa5d03859f1!2s1408+Rue+Burruntz%2C+64210+Bidart!5e0!3m2!1sfr!2sfr!4v1499850315148" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 89, 2, 'French-Gastronomy', '\r\nIt wonâ€™t take long before you realise the strong culture around the Basque Country cuisine due to the mix of both itâ€™s French and Spanish cultures and itâ€™s proximity to the sea and mountains. The Basque countries traditional meals are becoming more and more known around the world and all seem to be made in a traditional method passed on from generation to generation.\r\n<br>\r\nCome join us and enjoy 90 minutes of hands on cooking experience in our brand new fully equipped kitchen with our Basque Chef. Whether you are well accustomed to the kitchen or you are just starting out, we are sure you will learn and enjoy your experience. Participate at your own rhythm using seasonal and locally sourced products to prepare a delicious 3 course traditional Basque meal. Then sit back, relax and indulge in your master pieces with specifically chosen wine for the meal.\r\n<br>\r\nThe package\r\n\r\nBilingual and experimented Chef\r\nHands on cooking class\r\nDelicious 3 courses meal + wine\r\nGroup size 4 to 12 guests\r\nDuration: 2 h', 'Tuesday,Wednesday , Thursday and Friday on demand', 'BasqueCookingClassinBiarritz'),
