('', 'By night tour Dinner Cruise', 'Paris', '<iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2625.0033028466396!2d2.347590615117106!3d48.858147408678775!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x47e66e1e7a4bfd17%3A0xc20b2f8281bc79bc!2s3+Rue+Saint-Martin%2C+75004+Paris!5e0!3m2!1sfr!2sfr!4v1499851176938" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 328, 4, 'By-night', '\r\nDescription of the tour\r\n\r\nNo doubt about itâ€¦ the most touching time on your Parisian trip! Combine a tour on a 2CV and a dinner on a boat and your evening out will be magic!\r\n<br>\r\nYour evening will begin at the door of your hotel. A private driver will take you for a pure relaxation, right in the heart of Paris for one hourâ€¦Champs ElysÃ©es, Eiffel Tower, Notre Dame, Pyramid of Louvre...\r\n<br>\r\nProlong this sweet timeâ€¦ a dinner-cruise is ready for you with "les Bateaux Parisiens" ! A two hours and a half magic orchestrated by a singer and her three musiciansâ€¦dÃ©cor, refined table arts, privacy of small tables, dance-floor full of life...all the ingredients for a delightful evening.\r\n<br>\r\nYou stop in front of Notre Dame for a moving â€œAve Mariaâ€, the lovers kiss and make a wish under Pont Marie, Eiffel Tower sparkles...just magic!\r\n\r\n<br>\r\nItinerary of the tour *\r\n\r\nAvenue des Champs ElysÃ©es - Concorde - Arc de Triomphe - TrocadÃ©ro - Tour Eiffel - Invalides - Pont Alexandre 3 - Petit et Grand Palais - Pyramide du Louvre - Opera Garnier(1h)+ dinner cruise by night on the seine (2h30) - return not included after the cruise\r\n\r\n<br>\r\nPICK UP IN PARIS CENTER : FROM YOUR HOTEL OR ADDRESS IN PARIS CENTER\r\nTHE DRIVERS : FUN, PARISIAN, PROFESSIONAL & ENGLISH SPEAKING\r\nCITROEN 2CV CAR : CONVERTIBLE & TRANSPARENT ROOF', 'Every evenings', 'By night tour + dinner cruise'),
