('', 'Cooking class in Paris Menu Bistrot', 'Paris', '<iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2623.523023322316!2d2.291104315118289!3d48.88636870669122!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x47e66f9060e2083b%3A0x20903d46cd667f78!2s11+Avenue+St%C3%A9phane+Mallarm%C3%A9%2C+75017+Paris!5e0!3m2!1sfr!2sfr!4v1499851356267" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 99, 3, 'French-Gastronomy', 'English cooking class in Paris: Menu Bistrot.\r\n<br>\r\nWith our English cooking classes in Paris, discover the preparation of a full French gastronomic menu.\r\nFrench cuisine is diverse, elegant, tasty and thatâ€™s what makes his fame. With our english cooking classes in Paris, discover the preparation of a full french gastronomic menu. With the advice of our chef, you can easily replicate this menu and ravish your entourage.\r\n<br>\r\nYou will experience this french Bistro menu through the teachings of our specialized and english speaking chef, as if you were in a famous Paris bistro.\r\n<br>\r\nFirst course: Beef tartare\r\n<br>\r\nMain course: Breast of duck with honey and spices, spinach with olive oil\r\n<br>\r\nDessert : Chocolat â€œfondantâ€ with vanilla cream\r\nTake time to relax and have fun with our English cooking classes in Paris, with Le Labo Culinaire.\r\n<br>\r\nAll ingredients and Kitchenware useful for the workshop are provided by Le Labo Culinaire.', 'Monday on Friday ', 'Cooking class in Paris'),
