('', 'Dinner at a local s home in Biarritz', 'Biarritz', '<iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2895.138636573909!2d-1.5683992850933193!3d43.47857707172388!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0xd516b2e902d71c5%3A0xe4e412e1794c4ac!2s9+Boulevard+du+Prince+de+Galles%2C+64200+Biarritz!5e0!3m2!1sfr!2sfr!4v1499853433288" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 119, 3, 'French-Gastronomy', '\r\nDinner at a localâ€™s in Biarritz\r\n<br>\r\nTake a break from being a tourist and become one with the Basque culture. Come dine at Philibertâ€™s house.\r\n<br>\r\nPhilibert, a chef by trade, will open his home to you and treat you to some of the Basque Countries most delicious and traditional meals. A three course meal, using seasonal and local products will be served and paired with the perfect wine.\r\n<br>\r\nPhilibertâ€™s home is situated over the beautiful â€œCotes des Basquesâ€ beach in Biarritz and is only a short stroll from the town centre and also an easy location to arrive by Taxi. Philibert has a wealth of knowledge on both French and the Basque cuisine and culture and will surely provide you with some good laughs and entertainment over your dinner.\r\n<br>\r\nThe package\r\n<br>\r\nHost and Chef (French, English and Spanish speaking)\r\nDelicious 3 course meal + wine\r\nBeautiful location with ocean view\r\nGroup size 4 to 6 guests\r\nDuration: 2.5 hours', 'Thursday Only', 'DINNER AT A LOCALâ€™S HOME IN BIARRITZ'),
