('', 'Evening Jazz Trip', 'Paris', '', 250, 1, 'By-night', '\r\n\r\nStart your evening with a charming Parisian 2CV ride followed by a concert at the Duc des Lombards Jazz Club! \r\n<br>\r\nYour chauffeur and his 2CV will welcome you at the door of your hotel. You embark on a ride of 1 hour in the streets of Paris. After this delightful trip your driver will drop you in the center of Paris boulevard Sebastopol to continue your evening with the rhythms of the Jazzy Parisian nights at the Duc des Lombards! New decor, new sound, new comfort: the Duc des Lombards welcomes you in an intimate atmosphere Jazzy close to the scene to enjoy a moment of pure pleasure. \r\n<br>\r\n(this service includes: departure from your hotel at 20.30 - 1h ride in a 2CV - drop off at the Lombard Duke - Jazz concert at 22h - a glass of champagne per person) ( not include: the return after the concert) \r\n<br>\r\n- OFFER ONLY AVAILABLE MONDAY THROUGH FRIDAY - \r\n<br>\r\nItinerary of the tour *\r\n\r\nAvenue des Champs Elysees - Concorde - Arc de Triomphe - Trocadero - Tour Eiffel - Invalides - Pont Alexandre 3 - Petit et Grand Palais - Pyramide du Louvre - Opera Garnierâ€¦(1h)+ Jazz show (not include: the return after the concert\r\n\r\n<br>\r\nPICK UP IN PARIS CENTER : FROM YOUR HOTEL OR ADDRESS IN PARIS CENTER\r\nTHE DRIVERS : FUN, PARISIAN, PROFESSIONAL & ENGLISH SPEAKING\r\nCITROEN 2CV CAR : CONVERTIBLE & TRANSPARENT ROOF', 'Every day', 'Evening Jazz'),
