('', 'Geneve et son lac', 'Haute-Savoie', '<iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d44180.32009208754!2d6.108983172252253!3d46.20508353014114!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x478c650693d0e2eb%3A0xa0b695357b0bbc39!2zR2Vuw6h2ZSwgU3Vpc3Nl!5e0!3m2!1sfr!2sfr!4v1501845251501" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 0, 0, 'Visites', 'Geneva\'s rich history is not only a jet of water in the heart of Lake Geneva is a city with a strong atmosphere. Its old town clustered around its cathedral, museums with eclectic collections, parks and gardens sumptuous make it a city where the visits are readily lend themselves to strolling. Here ancient history and contemporary history intersect at every moment of our peregrinations.', '', 'Geneve et son lac'),
