('', 'Montmartre Gourmet and Parisian life', 'Paris', '<iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2623.5322478969756!2d2.3408954508569426!3d48.886192879188584!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x47e66e432e04c811%3A0xc63ce48b5005548d!2sMontmartre!5e0!3m2!1sfr!2sfr!4v1501602200507" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 265, 3, 'Visites', 'Our tour will start at the cabaret Moulin Rouge. We will walk up the hilly streets of Lepic, Caulaincourt and Abbesses, where the Montmartre best gourmet shops are located. During this part of the tour, you will learn how to navigate through the vast variety of products. We will talk about the French culinary traditions and explore why France is so particular about its food and wines. For tasting part of the tour, we will visit a typical Montmartre apartment, where you will have a unique opportunity to see the Parisian live and habits.\r\n\r\nAfter the tour, you are welcome to stay in Montmartre and continue on to the Paintersâ€™ Square and the Sacred Heart basilica.', 'Tous les jours', 'Montmartre Gourmet and Parisian life'),
