('', 'Private bike tour Marie Antoinette', 'Paris', '<iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2624.7918216304256!2d2.3507548151172935!3d48.8621800083949!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x47e66e1b991f6245%3A0xd43e49560a39afb7!2s13+Rue+Brant%C3%B4me%2C+75003+Paris!5e0!3m2!1sfr!2sfr!4v1499860253504" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 280, 3, 'Bike', 'Private bike tour Marie-Antoinette\r\nFollow the unpredictable life of Marie Antoinette â€“ Where will it lead ?\r\n<br>\r\nEverything started out well â€“ she was young, rich and pretty.\r\n<br>\r\nThroughout your visit your National Guide will reveal why Marie Antoinette would become so reviled and hated to the point of becoming a welcomed victim of the guillotine.\r\n<br>\r\nMarie Antoinette is synonymous with the Palace of Versailles. But Paris was where the most dramatic events of her life took place. With your Paris Bike Tour guide you will discover it all: From Marie Antoinetteâ€™s grandiose wedding at lâ€™HÃ´tel de Ville, her wild escapades at the Galeries du Palais Royal and her final imprisonment at the Conciergerie.\r\n<br>\r\nOn this tour of Paris by bike you will follow the life of the most famous Queen of France.\r\n\r\n<br>\r\nSights and stops \r\nPlace de lâ€™HÃ´tel de Ville\r\nRue des Halles - Place des Victoires\r\nJardins et Galeries du Palais Royal\r\nCour du Carrousel Tuileries\r\nPlace de la Concorde\r\nPont Neuf : Ã©vocation FÃªte de la FÃ©dÃ©ration (Tour Eiffel),\r\nLa Conciergerie\r\nIle de la CitÃ©\r\nQuai des OrfÃ¨vres, parvis Jean-Paul II , rue dâ€™Arcole, pont dâ€™Arcole\r\nQuai de Gesvres â€“ rue des Archives\r\nHÃ´tel de Rohan\r\nCarreau du Temple Square du Temple\r\n<br>\r\nThe price of this visit include\r\nBicycle\r\nAccessories: helmet, basket, poncho\r\nInsurance\r\nNot included: Refreshments, snacks and drinks at well-earned breaks\r\n<br>\r\nAvailable in English French and German', 'Every day