('', 'Street Art of Marseille', 'Marseille', '<iframe src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d185895.01266426005!2d5.264709552713976!3d43.28055461781579!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x12c9bf4344da5333%3A0x40819a5fd970220!2sMarseille!5e0!3m2!1sfr!2sfr!4v1501582322428" width="600" height="450" frameborder="0" style="border:0" allowfullscreen></iframe>', 150, 2, 'Visites', 'With an attentive look you will see that the streets, walls and gates of Marseille make this Mediterranean city a gallery of contemporary art in the open sky.\r\nBecause of the distance between the various districts which have a considerable number of works, we are obliged to offer 2 separate guided tours, one around the Cours Julien and the other in the Panier district.\r\n', 'Tous les jours', 'Street Art of Marseille'),
