('Suite Jardin', 2, 37, '1 lit king size ', 'Demeure des Sacres', 228, '15:00:00', '11:00:00', 'Situated on the second floor by our house, it is reached by a lovely stairway.\r\n\r\nWith over 37 sq m, this beige and taupe coloured suite is very restful with its view over the garden. You can also relax in the lounge.\r\n\r\nYou may also enjoy the private bathroom with its balneo shower.\r\n\r\nComposed of a bedroom and a lounge, it can receive a couple and two children, or two couples.\r\n\r\n\r\nEquipments\r\nA 180 x 200 cm King Size bed,\r\nTwo easy chairs in the main bedroom (21 sq m),\r\nA sofa as well as a comfortable convertible chair-bed,\r\nA private 8 sq m shower-room (120 x 100 cm shower, washbasin, towel radiator, hair dryer),\r\nPrivate toilets,\r\n80 cm flat screen TV (TNT and international channels via satellite),\r\nSmall desk\r\nFree Wifi access,\r\nMini-bar and courtesy tray,\r\nSafe.', 'Suite Jardin.jpg', 1, 1, 1, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 1, 0, 1),
