('Suite Royale - 2 Persons', 5, 46, 'Lits doubles et lits simples', 'Demeure des Sacres', 253, '15:00:00', '11:00:00', 'With 46 sq m, this is the largest of our bedrooms and can receive up to five guests.\r\n\r\nOn the first floor of our hotel, it is reached by a lovely stairway. It is fitted with a beautiful wooden floor and a white marble fireplace in the private lounge.\r\n\r\nIts high windows, fitted with electric blinds, give access to the balcony where you can enjoy the magnificent view over the Cathedral.\r\n\r\nThe view onto the faÃ§ade of the Cathedral from its terrace is unique right in the city centre of Reims.\r\n\r\nComposed of a bedroom and a lounge, it can receive a couple and three children or two couples.\r\n\r\nEquipments\r\n\r\nA 180 x 200 cm King Size bed,\r\nTwo easy chairs in the main bedroom (24 sq m),\r\nA sofa as well as a comfortable convertible chair-bed,\r\nA private 10 sq m bathroom (claw-foot bathtub, 100 x 100 cm shower, towel radiator, hair-dryer),\r\nPrivate toilets,\r\n80 cm flat screen TV (TNT and international channels via satellite),\r\nSmall desk\r\nFree wifi access,\r\nMini-bar and courtesy tray,\r\nSafe.', 'Suite Royale - 2 Persons.jpg', 1, 1, 1, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 1, 0, 1),
