('Suite Superieure avec Terrasse', 2, 38, 'Lit double', 'Villa Stephanie', 120, '15:00:00', '11:00:00', 'This suite of 38 m2 with independent entrance is located on the ground floor of the villa, has a sitting area, Italian shower, toilet\r\n\r\nDesk, TV, garden furniture, air-conditioning, Nespresso coffee machine, kettle, bathrobe, hairdryer, slippers, towels, pool towels and welcome products.\r\n\r\nA bed 180 x 200 (Or twin beds on request)\r\n\r\nBreakfast Included.\r\n', 'Suite Superieure avec Terrasse.jpg', 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1),
('The Cottage', 4, 18, 'Lit double et canapÃ©-lit', 'Manoir de la Baronnie', 170, '15:00:00', '11:00:00', 'The cottage\r\n\r\nThis cute little nordic cottage located in the park of our property can accomodate 4 persons. Its surface is 20 m2 + a 6m2 mezzanine, and a 15 m2 terrace. it contains a double bed and two single beds, a bathroom with shower and toilets,  a little kitchen, and electric heating.', 'The Cottage.jpg', 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, 1),
('The Reims Bedroom', 2, 28, '1 lit king size ou 2 lits simple', 'Demeure des Sacres', 153, '15:00:00', '11:00:00', 'Located on the second floor of our hotel, from the landing you can admire the multi-coloured glass canopy letting in outside light.\r\n\r\nThis suite is composed of a hall giving out onto a bedroom and a private shower-room. It covers over 28 sq m.\r\n\r\nEquipments\r\n\r\nA 180 x 200 cm King Size bed (or two separate 90 x 200 cm beds, please specify when booking),\r\nTwo easy chairs,\r\nOne private shower-room (120 x 100 cm shower, washbasin, towel radiator, hair dryer),\r\nPrivate toilets,\r\n80 cm flat screen TV (TNT and international channels via satellite),\r\nFree Wifi access,\r\nMini-bar and courtesy tray,\r\nSafe.', 'The Reims Bedroom.jpg', 1, 1, 1, 1, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 1),
('Thym', 4, 40, 'Lit double et canapÃ©-lit', 'La Maison des Aromes', 130, '15:00:00', '11:00:00', 'On the first floor, with entrance from a shared terrace, these two very large rooms each have a king- size bed (180x200cm) and a double sofa-bed(140x200cm)and a spectacular view over the hills.\r\n\r\nLa Maison des ArÃ´mes has 5 rooms, each with private entrance, bathroom, terrace, free WiFi, TV and air conditioning.\r\nPrivate parking is available for all guests.\r\nRoom prices include a full breakfast â€“ served in your room or on the terrace.', 'Thym.jpg', 1, 0, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1),
('Vinalia', 2, 40, 'Lit double ou lits jumeaux', 'Chateau Meyre', 160, '15:00:00', '11:00:00', 'This superior room, located on the first floor of the chateau has a panoramic vineyards view. the bathroom is equipped with a bathtub.\r\nking size or twin beds.\r\n\r\n', 'Vinalia.jpg', 1, 0, 0, 1, 0, 1, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 1);
